{"tid":32210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"工展會變CY歡送會 大陽如常升起但張曉明甩底","createTime":"2016-12-10T05:26:24.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T18:53:36.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9542bed4ce5515a3e497b098150b35d116728995","tid":32210,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:26:24.000Z","msg":"第51屆工展會周六開幕，昨日突然宣佈不角逐連任的特首梁振英亦有偕同太太梁唐青儀出席。2年前佔領期間曾指「大陽如常升起」的中聯辦主任張曉明，原本答允出席，惟大會指昨日早上收到通知，張曉明今日不會出席，改由副主任殷曉靜到場。<br />\n<br />\n活動期間梁振英與太太在現場購物，共花費了2230.5港元，其中在一個社企攤檔購買了一個$790元印有「那怕再重」的紅白藍膠袋，二人離開時未有回應記者提問。<br />\n<br />\n廠商會會長李秀恒致詞時提到特首梁振英每年都有出席工展會，他的支持十分重要，對於梁昨日宣布不競選感到突然，未知他明年會否再出席工展會活動，至於廠商會意屬哪位特首候選人，他表示會會憑政綱認真考慮，會支持愛國愛港和乎合基本法的參選人。"},{"pid":"6129e442c08c2230558fd667435b96f6309f6ad8","tid":32210,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:27:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小明去咗邊？"},{"pid":"26ac6f60f61f26b39f2689b03c5c0d63eaa9a799","tid":32210,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:44:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小明去咗邊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n雙規？"},{"pid":"14e3e8103b9b3875cdd559a9dbef4e0c72bdee87","tid":32210,"uid":22080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T05:44:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小明去咗邊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小明係咪被禁錮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f8c2315e59b8fb1c9d48f68df0937f0d7ade57","tid":32210,"uid":1424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:17:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小明去咗邊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去北京探祖父，去西京探外婆。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afc6c7abd4facc4841b6bc81d39a7b92575b795d","tid":32210,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:18:46.000Z","msg":"正皮係俾標題嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ca3b9ae7ae3bba117d8194ef2b2ae0c3ea9eb0","tid":32210,"uid":52451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T18:30:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小明去咗邊？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小明係咪被禁錮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n小明琴日同我上左深圳未番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20c3817779b1e5cced78f738aa4ab3a6f87958d","tid":32210,"uid":3253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T18:53:36.000Z","msg":"大陽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}